00:06:22.100 --> 00:06:23.100
Andra.

00:06:23.100 --> 00:06:24.100
Just incredible.

00:06:24.100 --> 00:06:27.490
And so, what we want to try to do with Surf

00:06:27.530 --> 00:06:30.790
is bring the social web to the masses.

00:06:30.840 --> 00:06:31.840
To my mom.

00:06:31.840 --> 00:06:32.840
