00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:50.380
And ways that bring those multiple protocols together.

00:06:50.380 --> 00:06:52.530
Like RSS, ActivityPub, and AppPr

00:06:52.570 --> 00:06:53.050
oto.

00:06:53.060 --> 00:06:56.730
And then publish those feeds to BlueSky and ultimately to

00:06:56.730 --> 00:06:57.500
the web.

00:06:57.500 --> 00:06:59.870
